{"tid":866754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度男妄想活埋3日可復活成神 獲救反詛咒警員","createTime":"2018-10-18T06:24:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T06:44:21.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3e05bcfbc0461e4bb46c4a6b2fac0428483b6fca","tid":866754,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181017/_2018101718494559363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181017%2F_2018101718494559363.jpg&h=527c7d43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">哈洛相信活埋3天後即可「復活成神」。網上圖片<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n印度男子哈洛（Tantrik Deeraj Kharol）早前聲稱受到上帝的感召，絕食4日後活埋自己，並相信3天後即可「復活成神」。他活埋8小時後，被警方救出及送院求醫，男子卻在醒來後詛咒警員及醫生。<br />\n<br />\n哈洛居於印度的拉賈斯坦邦，他早前聲稱受到感召，只要將自己活埋3天後就可以復活成神。因此，他不顧其他村民的勸阻，在活埋前4天開始絕食，並執意活埋自己，要更要求村民助他在寺廟旁邊挖出一個大坑。<br />\n<br />\n至上周四（11日），哈洛舉行盛大的「下葬儀式」，吸引大批村民幫忙及圍觀。由於引起村民廣泛討論，事件最終驚動警方，並決定插手阻止。<br />\n<br />\n哈洛活埋近8小時後終被救出，警方指他當時出現缺氧以及身體虛弱，甚至處於瀕死邊緣，需立即送院搶救。哈洛康復後，不但沒向警方道謝，反斥對方令他無法成為神，因而詛咒他們，「阻止我死的人都會失去居所、失去所有！」。<br />\n<br />\n哈洛的身體狀況已趨穩定，但警方表示會向他採取法律行動，以警告民眾不要輕信謠言及不明的儀式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181017/_2018101718494610481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181017%2F_2018101718494610481.jpg&h=ffc6d3e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181017/_2018101718494696943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181017%2F_2018101718494696943.jpg&h=40901085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/842917\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F842917&d=1VW3aCcIKcO1RNMqTwAeg%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b2837d27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F842917&h=5f0a11bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/842917</a>"},{"pid":"7b74a1c64f5250a2c3a68cc8909c2518c931cdc4","tid":866754,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"差佬做乜咁多事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}